把这段加在你当前回调里 `parseVAppHttpModel:` 之前就可以，先从 `self.dualApps` 找到对应 `vapp`，再把缺失字段补回 `requestedVapp`。

建议替换为：

```objc
[[WBNetworkManager defaultManager] getLatestVappInfoWithVappId:vappId oaaVersion:oaaVersion callback:^(WBVAppDetailHttpModel * _Nullable requestedVapp, NSError * _Nullable error) {
    if (error) {
        if (callbackHandler) callbackHandler(nil, actionErrorFail);
    } else {

        WBVAppModel *matchedDualApp = nil;
        for (WBVAppModel *item in self.dualApps) {
            if (item.vid == requestedVapp.vid) {
                matchedDualApp = item;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (matchedDualApp) {
            if (requestedVapp.name.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.name = matchedDualApp.name;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.track_id.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.track_id = matchedDualApp.trackId;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.bundle_id.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.bundle_id = matchedDualApp.bundleId;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.icon_url.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.icon_url = matchedDualApp.iconURL;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.subtitle.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.subtitle = matchedDualApp.subtitle;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.artist_name.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.artist_name = matchedDualApp.artistName;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.scheme.length == 0) {
                requestedVapp.scheme = matchedDualApp.scheme;
            }
            if (requestedVapp.reserve_count <= 0) {
                requestedVapp.reserve_count = matchedDualApp.reserveCount;
            }
            if (!requestedVapp.visible) {
                requestedVapp.visible = matchedDualApp.visible;
            }
        }

        WBVAppModel *vapp = [self parseVAppHttpModel:requestedVapp];
        [vapp updateWithVAppDetailModel:requestedVapp];
        if (vapp.userInfo == nil) {
            vapp.userInfo = [[WBVAppUserInfo alloc] init];
        }
        [WBEventManager logVappDownloadEvent:vapp];
        [self.myApps addObject:vapp];
        [self checkVAppStatusForInstallation:vapp];
        if (callbackHandler) callbackHandler(vapp, actionErrorSuccess);
    }
}];
```

如果你想更干净一点，也可以抽一个私有方法，例如：

```objc
- (void)fillMissingFieldsForDetailModel:(WBVAppDetailHttpModel *)detailModel fromDualApps:(NSArray<WBVAppModel *> *)dualApps;
```

这样 `getVAppWithId:`、其他 `getLatestVappInfoWithVappId` 的地方也能复用。  
如果你确认，我下一步可以继续帮你整理成“抽方法版”的最终代码。

